cesf.math

Class Complex

  • java.lang.Object
    • cesf.math.Complex

  • public class Complex
extends Object
    Class for complex numbers

    the complex numbers have the form a+bi (example 3+4i), where i is the square of the -1 and the base of the imaginary numbers

    the parts of a complex number are

      a= the real part b= the imaginary part

    with a camplex number you can calculate diferents operations. This class implements the most necesaries.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    alexandre
